<li id="cite_note-36"><b><a href="#cite_ref-36" title="">^</a></b> It has been noted that the courtyard pattern and techniques of flooring of Harappan houses has similarities to the way house-building is still done in some villages of the region. <a href="#Reference-Lal-2002" title="">(Lal 2002, pp. 93–95)</a></li>
